  "texts": [
    "Currently, Gemini 1.0 Pro, a cost and latency-optimized version of Gemini 1.0, has been integrated into the new Bard.",
    "Google has announced plans to make Gemini 1.0 Ultra accessible through Bard Advanced in early 2024 [47].",
    "For this study, we analyzed data from the legacy Bard tested between July 16 and October 2, 2023, and results obtained from Bard after December 6, 2023, for Gemini 1.0 Pro.",
    "While Gemini models offer multi-modal capabilities [46], our research is concentrated on the text-only variant of Gemini 1.0 as implemented in the new Bard.",
    "Moving forward, any mention of Gemini 1.0 Pro in this paper will refer specifically to the text-only iteration, excluding visual processing features."
